02:08:06,144 --> 02:08:09,565
Well, that's all right, Charlie.

1730
02:08:11,316 --> 02:08:14,278
Every family's got one
nowadays.

1731
02:08:44,266 --> 02:08:46,810
- That's it ?
- That's it.

1732
02:08:46,894 --> 02:08:49,646
- Take care of yourself, kid.
- All right, Manny. Thanks.

1733
02:08:55,694 --> 02:08:57,613
No, I'm not open.

1734
02:08:59,865 --> 02:09:02,201
