1735
02:09:03,869 --> 02:09:08,290
So, uh, you'll be
all right, huh ?

1736
02:09:08,373 --> 02:09:11,001
I'll be fine.

1737
02:09:12,127 --> 02:09:14,421
All right.

1738
02:09:14,505 --> 02:09:17,591
- [ Bell Ringing ]
- What's that ?

1739
02:09:19,426 --> 02:09:21,345
Uh, that's first bell.

1740
02:09:22,804 --> 02:09:25,849
