Just over the bridge.
- We'll find it.

1747
02:10:04,847 --> 02:10:06,890
Good-bye, Charlie.

1748
02:10:08,517 --> 02:10:10,435
Good-bye, Colonel.

1749
02:10:13,939 --> 02:10:15,858
Come here, son.

1750
02:10:31,623 --> 02:10:33,834
Okay, Manny.

1751
02:11:47,866 --> 02:11:49,952
George. George !

1752
02:12:28,699 --> 02:12:31,743
I called an open meeting
of this institution this morning...

1753
02:12:31,827 --> 02:12:35,289
because the incident that
occurred this Tuesday last...

1754
02:12:35,330 --> 02:12:39,418
describes an issue
that concerns all of us.

1755
02:12:40,961 --> 02:12:44,256
Not an isolated case
of vandalism, what happened...

1756
02:12:44,298 --> 02:12:48,844
is a symptom
of the sickness of a society,

1757
02:12:48,927 --> 02:12:52,848
a sickness which runs
counter to the principles...

1758
02:12:52,931 --> 02:12:54,850
this school was founded on,

1759
02:12:56,810 --> 02:13:02,024
