in the White House.

1761
02:13:05,027 --> 02:13:08,155
Baird men have run state departments
and investment houses,

1762
02:13:08,238 --> 02:13:12,367
founded department stores
and coached football teams.

1763
02:13:12,451 --> 02:13:16,163
Our alumni receive their bulletins
in ashrams in India...

1764
02:13:16,246 --> 02:13:18,165
and in palaces
in Jordan.

1765
02:13:18,248 --> 02:13:20,459
We are, in fact,
known around the world...

1766
02:13:20,501 --> 02:13:23,295
as the cradle
of this country's leadership.

1767
02:13:23,337 --> 02:13:25,923
- A beacon in the nation's --
- What are you doing here ?

1768
02:13:26,006 --> 02:13:28,967
- Got room for me up there, Charlie ?
- But today,

1769
02:13:29,051 --> 02:13:32,012
- We are bleeding from disrespect,
- Yeah, I guess so.

1770
02:13:32,054 --> 02:13:36,141
- Give us a hand.
- disrespect for our values...

1771
02:13:36,225 --> 02:13:39,978
