with no real witness.

1856
02:19:53,477 --> 02:19:57,356
Mr. Willis's testimony is
not only vague, it is unsubstantiated.

1857
02:19:57,397 --> 02:20:00,359
The substance I was
looking for, Mr. Simms,

1858
02:20:00,400 --> 02:20:02,903
was to come from you.

1859
02:20:05,864 --> 02:20:07,824
I'm sorry.

1860
02:20:08,951 --> 02:20:11,703
I'm sorry too, Mr. Simms,

1861
02:20:11,745 --> 02:20:14,206
because you know
what I'm going to do,

1862
02:20:14,248 --> 02:20:16,583
inasmuch as I can't punish
Mr. Havemeyer,

1863
