Mr. Potter or Mr. Jameson ?

1864
02:20:18,836 --> 02:20:20,963
And I won't punish
Mr. Willis.

1865
02:20:21,046 --> 02:20:23,465
He's the only party
to this incident...

1866
02:20:23,549 --> 02:20:26,510
who is still worthy of
calling himself a Baird man.

1867
02:20:27,886 --> 02:20:31,056
I'm going to recommend to
the Disciplinary Committee...

1868
02:20:32,140 --> 02:20:34,101
that you be expelled.

1869
02:20:34,142 --> 02:20:36,979
Mr. Simms, you are
a cover-up artist...

1870
02:20:37,062 --> 02:20:38,981
and you are a liar.

1871
02:20:39,064 --> 02:20:41,149
But not a snitch !

1872
02:20:41,233 --> 02:20:43,735
Excuse me ?

1873
02:20:43,819 --> 02:20:45,571
No, I don't
think I will.

1874
02:20:45,654 --> 02:20:50,242
- Mr. Slade.
- This is such a crock of shit !

1875
02:20:50,284 --> 02:20:53,161
[ Trask ] Please watch your
language, Mr. Slade.

1876
02:20:53,245 --> 02:20:56,164
You are in the Baird school,
not a barracks.

1877
02:20:56,248 --> 02:20:59,418
Mr. Simms, I will give you one
final opportunity to speak up.

1878
02:20:59,459 --> 02:21:02,004
Mr. Simms
doesn't want it.

1879
02:21:02,087 --> 02:21:04,006
He doesn't need
to be labeled...

1880
02:21:04,089 --> 02:21:06,758
