being a Baird man."

1881
02:21:06,800 --> 02:21:08,760
What the hell
is that ?

1882
02:21:08,802 --> 02:21:10,762
What is your motto here ?

1883
02:21:10,804 --> 02:21:15,058
"Boys, inform on your
classmates, save your hide;

1884
02:21:15,142 --> 02:21:18,020
anything short of that,
we're gonna burn you at the stake" ?

1885
02:21:18,103 --> 02:21:20,856
Well, gentlemen,

1886
02:21:20,939 --> 02:21:24,109
when the shit hits the fan,
some guys run...

1887
02:21:24,193 --> 02:21:26,153
