preparin' these minnows for manhood,

1902
02:22:05,734 --> 02:22:07,694
you better think again,

1903
02:22:07,736 --> 02:22:10,697
because I say you are
killin' the very spirit...

1904
02:22:10,739 --> 02:22:12,908
this institution
proclaims it instills.

1905
02:22:12,991 --> 02:22:15,994
