1913
02:22:39,226 --> 02:22:42,229
You don't know what
out of order is, Mr. Trask.

1914
02:22:42,312 --> 02:22:44,731
I'd show you,
but I'm too old,

1915
02:22:44,815 --> 02:22:47,234
I'm too tired,
too fuckin' blind.

